出售前需要将域名转移到属于您的脚本地址，并等待约两天，再发送交易进行确认或取消。确认的域名可以进行下一步，取消则会回到原来的状态。

The Market uses the protocol specifications of HIP-001 and HIP-006 to realize decentralized name transactions, and the transactions are on the chain to ensure the security of names.
1. Preparation for sale - locking the name

Before selling, you need to transfer the name to the script address belonging to you and wait about two days before sending the transaction for finalize or cancel. A finalized name can proceed to the next step, while a cancellation will return to the original status.
After confirming locking, you can ask a bid on the name, and the bid can be changed at any time during the sale.
During the process of sale, buyers can offer their desired price and the list of bids will be displayed in the name details.
During the sale, the buyer can buy the name directly at the buy it now price, and the sale will be completed after the transaction is on the chain.
While waiting for others to buy, they may also make a counter offer on the name; the counter offer will be listed in the name details, you may also accept the offer and complete the sale directly.

Note: After accepting the offer, the actual HNS received will be slightly less than the offer price, because two parts of it will be deducted: 0.5% service fee charged by FxWallet and the transaction on-chaining fee.
During the period, you can also cancel the sale. Unlock the name and wait for about two days, then you can confirm the unlocking.
Note: Unlocking can only be confirmed, not cancelled. If you change your mind, you need to confirm the unlocking first and then re-lock.

Now, your domain name is locked successfully. You can continue to ask a bid on the name.
The "unlock" operation is to cancel the sale.
The Market will list all names currently for sale, and the specific sale status will perform in the name detail.
If you are not satisfied with the bid price, you can also make a counter-offer by entering your desired price and waiting for confirmation from the seller; the bid can be modified at any time.

Note: Since the transaction is completely decentralized, each bid will require you to have a UTXO with just the right price. Therefore, if there is no current UTXO that meets the conditions, you will first send a transaction to yourself to integrate the right UTXO, and this process will be on the chain and consume the handling fee.

Note: The bid does not go on the chain, so in effect the UTXO can still be spent. We try to ensure that you pay for unbid UTXO first, and if you have to use them, you will be prompted before you pay. If you see the prompt and choose to spend it anyway, the previous bid will be invalid.
You can also choose to buy the name directly, you will pay the buy it now price plus a service fee of HNS to successfully purchase the name.
After a successful purchase, you need to wait for about two days and then make a purchase finalize. After the finalization, the name will officially belong to you.

The Market uses the protocol specifications of HIP-001 and HIP-006 to realize decentralized name transactions, and the transactions are on the chain to ensure the security of names.
1. Preparation for sale - locking the name

Before selling, you need to transfer the name to the script address belonging to you and wait about two days before sending the transaction for finalize or cancel. A finalized name can proceed to the next step, while a cancellation will return to the original status.
After confirming locking, you can ask a bid on the name, and the bid can be changed at any time during the sale.
During the process of sale, buyers can offer their desired price, and the list of bids will be displayed in the name details.
During the sale, the buyer can buy the name directly at the buy it now price, and the sale will be completed after the transaction is on the chain.
While waiting for others to buy, they may also make a counter offer on the name; the counter offer will be listed in the name details, you may also accept the offer and complete the sale directly.

Note: After accepting the offer, the actual HNS received will be slightly less than the offer price because two parts of it will be deducted: 0.5% service fee charged by FxWallet and the transaction on-chaining fee.
During the period, you can also cancel the sale. Unlock the name and wait for about two days; then you can confirm the unlocking.
Note: Unlocking can only be confirmed, not canceled. If you change your mind, you need to confirm the unlocking first and then re-lock.

Now, your domain name is locked successfully. You can continue to ask a bid on the name.
The "unlock" operation is to cancel the sale.
The Market will list all names currently for sale, and the specific sale status will perform in the name detail.
If you are not satisfied with the bid price, you can also make a counter-offer by entering your desired price and waiting for confirmation from the seller; the bid can be modified at any time.

Note: Since the transaction is completely decentralized, each bid will require you to have a UTXO with just the right price. Therefore, if there is no current UTXO that meets the conditions, you will first send a transaction to yourself to integrate the right UTXO, and this process will be on the chain and consume the handling fee.

Note: The bid does not go on the chain, so in effect the UTXO can still be spent. We try to ensure that you pay for unbid UTXO first, and if you have to use them, you will be prompted before you pay. If you see the prompt and choose to spend it anyway, the previous bid will be invalid.
You can also choose to buy the name directly; you will pay the buy it now price plus a service fee of HNS to successfully purchase the name.
After a successful purchase, you need to wait for about two days and then finalize the purchase. After the finalization, the name will officially belong to you.

Operasi ini memotong 0,5% dari biaya layanan (dibebankan oleh FxWallet) dan biaya prabayar dari transaksi. Anda akan menerima jumlah yang dipotong setelah transaksi selesai. Pastikan Anda menerima harga ini.
Market menggunakan spesifikasi protokol HIP-001 dan HIP-006 untuk mewujudkan transaksi nama yang terdesentralisasi, dan transaksi berada pada rantai untuk memastikan keamanan nama.

Sebelum menjual, Anda perlu mentransfer nama ke alamat skrip yang dimiliki oleh Anda dan menunggu sekitar dua hari sebelum mengirimkan transaksi untuk disetujui atau dibatalkan. Nama yang disetujui dapat melanjutkan ke langkah berikutnya, sementara pembatalan akan kembali ke status asal.
Setelah mengonfirmasi penguncian, Anda dapat mengajukan penawaran untuk nama tersebut, dan penawaran dapat diubah kapan saja selama proses penjualan.
Selama proses penjualan, pembeli dapat menawarkan harga yang diinginkan, dan daftar penawaran akan ditampilkan dengan rincian nama.
Selama penjualan, pembeli dapat membeli nama langsung pada harga "beli sekarang," dan penjualan akan selesai setelah transaksi dilakukan di rantai (chain).

Selama menunggu orang lain untuk membeli, mereka juga dapat membuat tawaran balik atas nama tersebut; tawaran balik akan tercantum dalam rincian nama, Anda juga dapat menerima tawaran tersebut dan menyelesaikan penjualan secara langsung.

Catatan: Setelah menerima penawaran, jumlah sebenarnya dari HNS yang diterima akan sedikit kurang dari harga penawaran karena dua bagian akan dikurangkan: biaya layanan 0,5% yang dibebankan oleh FxWallet dan biaya transaksi on-chaining.
Selama periode tersebut, Anda juga dapat membatalkan penjualan. Buka kunci nama tersebut dan tunggu sekitar dua hari; kemudian Anda dapat mengkonfirmasi pembukaan kunci.
Catatan: Pembukaan hanya dapat dikonfirmasi, tidak dapat dibatalkan. Jika Anda berubah pikiran, Anda perlu mengonfirmasi pembukaan terlebih dahulu dan kemudian mengunci kembali.

Sekarang, nama domain Anda telah berhasil dikunci. Anda dapat melanjutkan untuk mengajukan penawaran atas nama tersebut.
Operasi "buka kunci" adalah untuk membatalkan penjualan.
Market akan mencantumkan semua nama yang saat ini dijual, dan status penjualan spesifik akan muncul di detail nama.
